  "body": "**🧐 Motivation**\r\nSafeCast error messages are very large (even throwing a linter warning on default solhint settings.\r\n\r\nBecause Solidity is an error message hog, and I don't believe it does error message mapping yet, best to reduce the error message size to something more reasonable.\r\n\r\n** Proposed **\r\n\r\n`SafeCast: value doesn\\'t fit in 128 bits`\r\n\r\nto:\r\n\r\n`SafeCast: value > 128 bits`\r\n\r\n",
